message: "If you use this software, please cite both the software and the paper it implements."
title: "agent2model"
abstract: >-
  Compile a stable LangGraph/YAML agent procedure into a small open model's
  weights so it self-orchestrates with no runtime orchestrator, plus a
  procedure-adherence evaluation harness. An open implementation of Dennis et
  al. 2026 (arXiv:2605.22502).
type: software
